Package model

Class Price

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Price
  • public class Price
extends java.lang.Object
    Price object that determines the pricing of each ticket according to each criteria. Criteria consists of age group, and showtime date.

    2019-11-10
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
